{"tid":1306107,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"絕食手足要幫手！","createTime":"2019-07-11T04:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:28:11.000Z","uid":267654,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc2f659eef94cd1736b346b9bd19818f12dea85","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"真心求巴絲幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《招募絕食者支援團隊》<br />\n<br />\n各位，香港很多朋友也正運用不同方式抗爭中，我們的絕食運動已持續了超過170小時了，我們的絕食者體力即將進入臨界點。但至今，政府還沒有正面地回應我們的訴求，所以我們需要大家支持我們的絕食行動，協助絕食者基本的照顧，陪伴有需要的朋友，及回應來探訪的公眾等。<br />\n<br />\n我們希望招幕每天的場地支援人員：<br />\n- 到場協助絕食者表達絶食行動的意念<br />\n- 派發傳單/叫市民睇日記等<br />\n- 情緒支援/陪伴到場又有情緒的市民<br />\n- 幫手紀錄每位絕食者的身體status<br />\n- 每日兩更：12:00-14:00／17:00-21:00<br />\n- 每更希望有3-4人<br />\n<br />\n絕食者照顧team<br />\n- 早上了解絕食者狀況 <br />\n- 幫手清潔絕食者現場<br />\n- 陪絕食者去廁所<br />\n- 晚上9:00陪絕食者去沖涼<br />\n- 每日三段時間： 10:00am／13:00pm-14:00pm／21:00-23:00pm <br />\n<br />\n*不需要每天到，也未必要留一整更，但希望集氣，讓絕食者有更多支援～<br />\n<br />\n可以幫手的朋友請填寫以下表格，以便我們再與你聯絡：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/AByV3fw7ez11f7B3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FAByV3fw7ez11f7B3A&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8523%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=625fb636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/AByV3fw7ez11f7B3A</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ae1274159b14ab603269858c8aa2d867851c05","tid":1306107,"uid":268855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:47:32.000Z","msg":"<code>我無嘢講 我要見律師 我唔解鎖電話</code>"},{"pid":"11c4f9c41edea843ef53bb8d7f4f05c3cc892afa","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:49:10.000Z","msg":"一齊支援手足，對準目標！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c062984dc85f587ec82029686c66ea07d6c0f862","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"另外溫馨提示：<br />\n大家探陳伯時請留意時間。探訪時間為下午12至2、晚上6至9。<br />\n<br />\n因不少朋友晚上十點半、十一點仍來探訪，他不捨得不招呼大家，引致阻礙他沖涼時間，而他多數會選擇不沖，這會引致傷口埋唔到口。有勞各位留意探訪時間，讓陳伯好好休養！"},{"pid":"70d066474091e4d98b983fe08a4a5e955825a3b5","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:03:50.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"7322f0fcb8d55caeaee87a2b98182d6457f6bd46","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:04:18.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20479cd8bbb178be2200569629535903c4ecb619","tid":1306107,"uid":276528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T06:07:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eeb51bb9fe75b4e51abcba3c2c7ac62c88928e3b","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"(拜託幫手廣傳。分享感染更多人一起抗爭，誓要政府回應！亦多救一自毀的人！按一下分享對行動有很大的作用！)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YIZ9ag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YIZ9ag&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8523%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=af377e23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YIZ9ag</a><br />\n<br />\n【記絕食行動及祈禱會】Day 8：<br />\n<br />\n整天絕食隊也忙於籌備晚上的記者會，畢竟我們希望把理念傳到地極。我們也要開會，並與傳訊部義工溝通。<br />\n<br />\n感恩有不少傳媒朋友到訪，更有過百市民到場支持，更有市民即場為我們站台舉牌支持，很有被支持的感覺。當我們講出心聲，部份市民卻在飲泣；當我們吶喊，市民熱烈的回應，讓這記招頓然變成了培靈會---培養心靈力量。<br />\n<br />\n我們得到了回應，最少3位朋友、包括張超雄議員加入了我們的絕食。那份同行的力量又再加增了！不少記者、朋友問我：絕食真的能動搖這個政府嗎？<br />\n<br />\n現在愈來愈多市民參與及關注絕食，政府所面對的壓力愈來愈大，我看見將有更大的可能。香港人，大家努力集集氣，求上主引領，將不可能變為可能！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳凱興傳道(roy)<br />\n好鄰舍北區教會<br />\n2019年7月11日<br />\n<br />\n#不撤就繼續絕食<br />\n#若你想放棄或要燃燒生命抗爭請到我這裡來<br />\n#金鐘海富中心KFC外<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥 Carrie Lam<br />\n<br />\nYou may say I am a dreamer, but I am not the only one. I hope someday you will join us, and the world will be as one.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【反送中絕食分享】現新增了一個Telegram頻道，以分享絕食過程中的點滴，同時作為資訊傳遞的渠道，方便同路人前來支援或探望: <a href=\"https://t.me/hungerstrike_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhungerstrike_hk&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8523%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=f1b8e521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hungerstrike_hk</a>"},{"pid":"b616c0d97fc434a795fd4c90c567e576c3fcd0a8","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:54:42.000Z","msg":"我們我宣言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUP5x05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUP5x05.png&h=4b1008fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gNF6k7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gNF6k7.png&h=c267e0f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f330e95420ad597aab624d00332888a68e9c6e4","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:55:45.000Z","msg":"為大家更新絕食人士資料，其中陳傳道已經絕食超過200小時，但政府仍未派人回應，我們將會繼續堅持戰鬥到底！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7joxXs7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7joxXs7.png&h=2056cdcd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLoqx1t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLoqx1t.png&h=11127dce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B5J6hs9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB5J6hs9.png&h=19b5fcaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzyJ38a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrzyJ38a.png&h=24e1d056&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cw5TGUQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcw5TGUQ.png&h=86da68e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Obu5x1w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FObu5x1w.png&h=ce34081a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJiqx1x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJiqx1x.png&h=8dc67cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDYxXtd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDYxXtd.png&h=8dc5b3dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5931f5963bc776e5e29d05d0cc69e6dc9d58f290","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"今晚有新的絕食人士阿Poon 加入，與香港同行！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBGcc1J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBGcc1J.png&h=fba0ea79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSYFmU3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSYFmU3.png&h=5614ea72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3b47ab6d29a566ea2e840289767305a3938b4d5","tid":1306107,"uid":227811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0be7c70dda23160eb7e2f8b595335ff54097bd3","tid":1306107,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c062984dc85f587ec82029686c66ea07d6c0f862","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"另外溫馨提示：<br />\n大家探陳伯時請留意時間。探訪時間為下午12至2、晚上6至9。<br />\n<br />\n因不少朋友晚上十點半、十一點仍來探訪，他不捨得不招呼大家，引致阻礙他沖涼時間，而他多數會選擇不沖，這會引致傷口埋唔到口。有勞各位留意探訪時間，讓陳伯好好休養！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:25:23.000Z","msg":"咩傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee038ebcf174983b5e18eb50a6add53b42a4bc04","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0be7c70dda23160eb7e2f8b595335ff54097bd3","tid":1306107,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c062984dc85f587ec82029686c66ea07d6c0f862","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"另外溫馨提示：<br />\n大家探陳伯時請留意時間。探訪時間為下午12至2、晚上6至9。<br />\n<br />\n因不少朋友晚上十點半、十一點仍來探訪，他不捨得不招呼大家，引致阻礙他沖涼時間，而他多數會選擇不沖，這會引致傷口埋唔到口。有勞各位留意探訪時間，讓陳伯好好休養！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:25:23.000Z","msg":"咩傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:30:17.000Z","msg":"右腳皮膚問題"},{"pid":"b93d39f0134f22043da377a169729f4c35f71e80","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:48:11.000Z","msg":"(拜託幫手廣傳。分享感染更多人一起抗爭，誓要政府回應！亦多救一自毀的人！按一下分享對行動有很大的作用！)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YNb7zu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YNb7zu&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8523%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=62ce859f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YNb7zu</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【記絕食行動及祈禱會】Day 9：中氣<br />\n<br />\n記者會翌日，部份網民質疑，絕食了7天的人，怎有可能如此有中氣、說話如此大聲？不知是否假絕食？<br />\n<br />\n若Google一下絕食，你會發現絕食最難捱是第三、四天，饑餓感、胃痛、乏力等徵狀就會出現，但過後身體會作出適應，運用儲備供應養份，忘記肚餓。<br />\n<br />\n若認識我久的人，一向知我講野中氣十足，在教會講壇宣講超過十年，週六、日連帶5場崇拜、8個小組也是日常之事。陳伯更是老當益壯的農夫。於我們而言，有中氣講野，其實是何等閒之事呢？我們將7天的精力，就用在這一時。<br />\n<br />\n當然，這是有代價要付上。今天感覺很疲乏，而我躺下多次也未得恢復，或許是把中氣用畢。休息了一天，體力好好多了。<br />\n<br />\n今次揾命搏，正因香港已到了關鍵的時間，既擁抱同路人，同心向暴政說不！再疲累也不怕！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳凱興傳道(roy)<br />\n好鄰舍北區教會<br />\n2019年7月12日<br />\n<br />\n#不撤就繼續絕食<br />\n#若你想放棄或要燃燒生命抗爭請到我這裡來<br />\n#金鐘海富中心KFC外<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥 Carrie Lam<br />\n<br />\nYou may say I am a dreamer, but I am not the only one. I hope someday you will join us, and the world will be as one.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【反送中絕食分享】現新增了一個Telegram頻道，以分享絕食過程中的點滴，同時作為資訊傳遞的渠道，方便同路人前來支援或探望: <a href=\"https://t.me/hungerstrike_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhungerstrike_hk&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8523%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=f1b8e521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hungerstrike_hk</a>"},{"pid":"493b2fd4895fa2c32453df1a61a6366ab1bb76f6","tid":1306107,"uid":267654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:20:50.000Z","msg":"我哋要手足幫手呀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fYLAjgA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfYLAjgA.png&h=eb7cc339&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a18dfc95d3d0c21f1220f544c89cc8733558515","tid":1306107,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"3bf22f510cb4f8af30cfa1797bc6ed32668180db","tid":1306107,"uid":57753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}